00:15:24.340 --> 00:15:27.009
Odstupite, to je naredba. Pythone?

00:15:27.552 --> 00:15:28.594
Pokret!

00:15:36.811 --> 00:15:37.936
Ja...

00:15:38.521 --> 00:15:39.521
Nisam znala.

00:15:40.273 --> 00:15:44.860
Neznanje nije isto što i nevinost,

00:15:45.528 --> 00:15:46.737
gospođice Lane.

00:16:13.931 --> 00:16:16.516
Ustaj! Na noge!

00:16:28.905 --> 00:16:30.614
Brzo. On dolazi.

00:16:43.753 --> 00:16:45.087
Prilazi, dvije milje.

00:16:45.880 --> 00:16:48.006
Prolazim Pythona... sada.

00:16:56.265 --> 00:16:57.432
Odlazimo!

00:17:04.857 --> 00:17:06.900
Meta naciljana.
-Napad odobren.

00:17:07.610 --> 00:17:08.860
Aktiviran i u dometu.

00:17:14.867 --> 00:17:15.867
Tri.

00:17:17.954 --> 00:17:19.996
Dva. Jedan.

